									<header>
										<h3>Public Transit Policy</h3>
									</header>
									<p>As someone who has been riding the city bus for almost eleven years, I am quite familiar with transit policy.  I am the person who would advocate for expansion, as well as legislation to help increase funding.  Closer to home, I care about the actual network and where vehicles run.</p>
                                    <p>Over my eleven years, I have ridden several agencies.  <strong>NOTE: with the lone exception of Hampton Roads Transit (where I sat on a committee several years ago), I have only been a <i>passenger</i> on board these agencies' services.</strong></p>
